data.title: VALORANT Champions Tour 2023: Game Changers Championship
data.meta_description: VCT 2023: Game Changers Championship is an offline Brazilian VAL tournament organized by Riot Games. This S-Tier tournament took place from Nov 28 to Dec 03 2023 featuring 8 teams competing over a total prize pool of $500,000 USD.
